Name: Change Location of .m64 Data

Scripts.Script:
D476A: [16, "Part 1 (DEFAULT: 007B)", hex]
D4772: [16, "Part 2 (DEFAULT: 0860)", hex]
D4786: [copy, D476A, D476C]
D478A: [copy, D4772, D4774]

//For XXXXXXXX, change the value to place you want the .m64 data to go
XXXXXXXX: [copy, 7B0860, 7CC6C0]

Description:
Changes the .m64 data location.
Default Location: 007B0860
Location used by most SM64 Editor Versions: 03E00000
